<item>
            <title>[LU-16748] comment in ll_swap_layouts_close() is outdated</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16748</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;mdc_close_layout_swap_pack() does not exist, so the following comment needs to be updated.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;&#160; &#160; /* Close the file and {swap,merge} layouts between inode &amp;amp; inode2.&lt;br/&gt;
&#160; &#160; &#160;* NB: lease lock handle is released in mdc_close_layout_swap_pack()&lt;br/&gt;
&#160; &#160; &#160;* because we still need it to pack l_remote_handle to MDT. */&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And mdt_close_swap_layouts() does not exists any more. So its declaration can be removed from mdt_internal.h.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
